pull.title: [DONTMERGE] test merge of unmerged libsecp256k1 patches
pull.body: Just to see how they interact with different platforms in Travis.

events.body: I'd love a link to some form of a changelog for your lib in the pull-requests :).
Perhaps the commit message could have a list of the changes in the body?
@luke-jr Yeah that's sufficient... for now every single upgrade of the lib was a black-box commit-msg wise ;).
@luke-jr It does have a summary of all squashed changes.
